    {
        "id": "utility-config-loader",
        "type": "tab",
        "label": "Utility: Config Loader",
        "disabled": false,
        "info": "Loads JSON config files from /config/ into global.config namespace.\n\nBEFORE USING:\n- Configure the 'Highland MQTT' broker node with hub IP and svc_nodered credentials\n- If you already have an MQTT broker config node, update the broker ID references\n  in the three MQTT nodes below to point to your existing broker node instead.\n\nTriggers:\n- Startup (0.5s delay after deploy)\n- Manual inject\n- MQTT: highland/command/config/reload            (full reload)\n- MQTT: highland/command/config/reload/{name}     (selective reload)\n\nValid {name} values: device_registry, flow_registry, notifications,\n                     thresholds, healthchecks, secrets"
    },
